code: @Test public void ofShouldReturnOriginCapableFieldError() {     FieldError fieldError = OriginTrackedFieldError.of(FIELD_ERROR, ORIGIN).     assertThat(fieldError.getObjectName()).isEqualTo("foo").     assertThat(fieldError.getField()).isEqualTo("bar").     assertThat(Origin.from(fieldError)).isEqualTo(ORIGIN). }

@Test public void toStringShouldAddOrigin() {     assertThat(OriginTrackedFieldError.of(FIELD_ERROR, ORIGIN).toString()).isEqualTo("Field error in object 'foo' on field 'bar': rejected value [null]" + ". codes []. arguments []. default message [faf]. origin afile"). }
